Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.99,0:01:14.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Squeez'n step on it hard
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.99,0:01:14.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}跨上机车 马力全开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.69,0:01:17.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try to feet my heart beat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.69,0:01:17.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}试着去感受心的律动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:21.28,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,High,as high as you can
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:21.28,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}飞跃吧！尽你所能！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.39,0:01:24.85,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All your blood will turn to fountain water
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.39,0:01:24.85,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}血液沸腾有如泉涌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:28.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded by plot in this universe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:28.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大千世界，我们的周遭布满陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.37,0:01:32.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wash away the stain of blood with tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.37,0:01:32.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}用泪水洗去血染的污点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.08,0:01:35.35,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot look,or they will spell on you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.08,0:01:35.35,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}让双眼避开所有的蛊惑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.38,0:01:38.80,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wind of fuego will lead us through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.38,0:01:38.80,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"烈焰"之风会引领我们向前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:55.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:55.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真实 我与它们融与一体
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:01:59.78,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found guide-in line in the raging world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:01:59.78,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在波涛汹涌的世界里找寻指引
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.82,0:02:03.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you see,in the sky,even in this insane world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.82,0:02:03.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}举目看 天湛蓝 纵然世界狂乱不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:05.12,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ride on Back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:05.12,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}仍有背骑的身影穿梭其间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:08.11,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All we need is your sympathy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:08.11,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我们需要的是你们的共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.13,0:02:11.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We make the history of our own
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.13,0:02:11.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}一同去创造属于我们的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.38,0:02:14.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
